# sphericalSpiral

- _sphericalSpiral(a)_

Answer the paramteric equation for the spherical spiral,
a special case of a loxodrome.

Plot:

~~~spl svg=A
(-6.pi -- 6.pi).functionPlot(
	400,
	0.1.sphericalSpiral
)
~~~

